headline.print_headline: US Striker Aron Johannsson Back in Form
headline.main: US Striker Aron Johannsson Back in Form

lead_paragraph: Aron Johannsson's opportunistic goal on a lunging header between two defenders in Dutch league action last weekend provided the latest evidence that he could emerge as an American scoring threat in Brazil this June.
